    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "bacitracin? i think i saw that at the guardian pharmacy earlier. is it safe to just use that a few times a day to clear it up quickly? and like for the saline flush, can i just use regular contact lens solution or does it have to be something else? i just want to get this sorted fast so i can get back to work.",
